{"tid":1827964,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌……","createTime":"2020-01-17T11:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T06:03:52.000Z","uid":152123,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d987086d7e86f16a6da570de5cdd1c7c6f680f9a","tid":1827964,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"cbecda257a6892a4bf1f62e6508da8a0ec8adb8a","tid":1827964,"uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"Sis你真係好勇敢..."},{"pid":"bbf84537eaf4059f3ca40eb7ad46b5108dfdc9eb","tid":1827964,"uid":136738,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"見到標題已經正平左<br />\nsis好波！"},{"pid":"c0b67b912c7505db1934d392a20c530a1487ad29","tid":1827964,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbecda257a6892a4bf1f62e6508da8a0ec8adb8a","tid":1827964,"uid":88491,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"Sis你真係好勇敢..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b95c000b38b55f3038c7ef2d93ba09f4e6e1c0","tid":1827964,"uid":199902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"119中環見"},{"pid":"50627930d0becb7b4a5d30642e203ee0cb51fd54","tid":1827964,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"1262e905506bfbffa0ed44c10a0cfc2710a4fdc8","tid":1827964,"uid":152123,"like":12,"